               <salute>Dear John,</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>How's life treating you? I've been enjoying my time in Spain, where I've had the
               pleasure of exploring the picturesque streets of Barcelona and indulging in
               delectable tapas in Madrid. Soon, I will be embarking on a journey to Italy, where I
               look forward to savoring authentic pasta in Rome, appreciating the magnificent art in
               Florence, and immersing myself in the rich culture that this country has to offer. I
               truly wish you were here to share in these incredible experiences.</p>      
            <closer>
               <salute>Wishing you all the best,</salute>
               <signed>Tomek</signed>
            </closer>
